dct_title_s:
Africa : Iuxta navigationes et observationes recentissimas aucta, correcta et in sua
          regna et status divisa, in lucem edita
dct_description_sm:
Cartouche includes natives, pyramids, animals, lighthouses and ships. "Enormous lakes
        are shown in Central Africa and the information about the southern extremity of the
        continent is largely fictitious."
